webpackJsonp([0x6ccf18f0628a],{641:function(e,a){e.exports={data:{profile:{id:"a40173e1-9745-53df-b894-83108e83162e",content:"<p>Music has always been Cliff’s first passion. Since 2012, he has been DJing various events in the New England area such as weddings, private events, and fundraisers. While attending college, he continued to grow his talents by DJing more events at various local Boston bars (West End Johnnies, The Harp and Ned Devine’s). In 2013 Cliff received an internship with DJ Maverik from Boston&#8217;s popular radio station, Jam’n 94.5. Cliff was able to work alongside Maverik at various events and gained more knowledge of on-air radio daily agendas.</p>\n<p>Cliff’s experience as a DJ/MC is noticed immediately. Cliff understands that he is not there to be the main attraction, but to let the music do most of the talking. Clients are consistently impressed with his professionalism and the energy that he brings to each event.</p>\n<p>He understands a crowd&#8217;s musical interests and always plays the precise music to keep everyone on the dance floor. He brings energy and excitement to every event, a strong knowledge of sound and lighting, and a personality that clients love. Cliff has a deep passion for his profession, which he hopes to someday share in the community by creating a youth DJ program<br />\nat local boys and girls clubs or youth centers.</p>\n<p>Cliff spins a tailored mix of Classics, Motown, Oldies, Hip Hop, R&amp;B, Top 40, Reggae, Reggaeton, House, Club hits, and fun music that will keep you dancing all night. If you’d like to chat with him about the possibilities please contact us directly and we’ll put you in touch!</p>\n",title:"Cliff Desrosena",acf:{title:"DJ, Emcee",video:"https://youtu.be/LiTrQvXOu5k?si=PMu1EA3AnJf8PMa5",facebook:"",instagram:"",testimonials:'<div class="content-block content-block-testimonial "><p><br />\nDJ Cliff was absolutely amazing to work with from start to finish. He was professional, easygoing, and totally understood the vibe we wanted for the night. During the reception, he read the room perfectly — the energy never dipped, and he had everyone on the dance floor all night long! So many of our guests commented on how incredible he was and how fun the music felt throughout the entire evening. The transitions, song choices, and pacing were spot on — it truly made our reception unforgettable. I can’t recommend DJ Cliff and C-Zone Entertainment enough. If you want a DJ who keeps the party going and creates the best atmosphere, he’s the one!<br />\n</p><p class="from">Stephanie and Michael, Tupper Manor, 10.17.25</p></div>\n<div class="content-block content-block-testimonial "><p><br />\nWe used C-Zone and DJ Cliff for our wedding reception! They were listed on our venue&#8217;s preferred client list and we are so grateful to have found them! Cliff was so great throughout the planning process &#8211; he fully understood the vibe we were going for and executed!! We also had a meeting a few weeks before our day where he played the different specific versions of the songs we wanted to use for our first and parent dances, which was so helpful and put us at ease to ensure a smooth night! Highly recommend DJ Cliff and the team at C-Zone!!<br />\n</p><p class="from">Lauren and Jarred, Granite Links, 9.27.25</p></div>\n<div class="content-block content-block-testimonial "><p><br />\nSimply put, DJ Cliff Desrosena and C-Zone Entertainment were amazing!! We hired C-Zone for our wedding on June 22, 2025, and we couldn’t be happier with our decision! From our very first interactions, Gina and DJ Cliff were professional, responsive, and genuinely enthusiastic about making our day special. In the planning phase, Cliff took the time to understand our music preferences, timeline, and overall vibe. He made helpful suggestions, listened to our plans and even accommodated our special requests, including music for the Hora. </p>\n<p>On the day of the wedding, Cliff was punctual, well-prepared, and brought incredible energy to the event. The ceremony music was timed perfectly, the cocktail hour had the perfect background ambiance, and once the reception started—WOW! The dance floor was packed the entire night. Our guests are still raving about how much fun they had. What really stood out to us was his ability to read the crowd and keep the energy flowing. The transitions between songs were seamless, and he kept everyone—from our younger nieces and nephews to our older relatives—dancing and smiling. We are so grateful to Cliff for helping create such unforgettable memories. Highly, highly recommend to any couple looking for an amazing wedding DJ!</p>\n<p></p><p class="from">Azhar and Samantha, The Barn at Gibbet Hill, 6.22.25</p></div>\n'},image:{localFile:{childImageSharp:{thumbnail:{base64:"data:image/jpeg;base64,",aspectRatio:1.5052754982415006,src:"/static/87a69f167d7902b025185ad1958d8498-7ea100c283443ce24364cd9be240a96a-d0643.jpg",srcSet:"/static/87a69f167d7902b025185ad1958d8498-7ea100c283443ce24364cd9be240a96a-2c2fe.jpg 110w,\n/static/87a69f167d7902b025185ad1958d8498-7ea100c283443ce24364cd9be240a96a-a2e2b.jpg 220w,\n/static/87a69f167d7902b025185ad1958d8498-7ea100c283443ce24364cd9be240a96a-d0643.jpg 440w,\n/static/87a69f167d7902b025185ad1958d8498-7ea100c283443ce24364cd9be240a96a-77eb3.jpg 660w,\n/static/87a69f167d7902b025185ad1958d8498-7ea100c283443ce24364cd9be240a96a-78eca.jpg 880w,\n/static/87a69f167d7902b025185ad1958d8498-7ea100c283443ce24364cd9be240a96a-38d87.jpg 1284w",sizes:"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px",originalImg:"/static/87a69f167d7902b025185ad1958d8498-7ea100c283443ce24364cd9be240a96a-38d87.jpg"},full:{src:"/static/87a69f167d7902b025185ad1958d8498-7ea100c283443ce24364cd9be240a96a-10d9a.jpg",height:266,width:400,srcSet:"/static/87a69f167d7902b025185ad1958d8498-7ea100c283443ce24364cd9be240a96a-10d9a.jpg 1x,\n/static/87a69f167d7902b025185ad1958d8498-7ea100c283443ce24364cd9be240a96a-738fa.jpg 1.5x,\n/static/87a69f167d7902b025185ad1958d8498-7ea100c283443ce24364cd9be240a96a-4042a.jpg 2x,\n/static/87a69f167d7902b025185ad1958d8498-7ea100c283443ce24364cd9be240a96a-935ac.jpg 3x"}}}},yoast:{title:"",canonical:"",metaDescription:"",linkdex:"",metakeywords:"",noIndex:"",noFollow:"",meta_robots_adv:"",metaKeywords:"",redirect:"",ogTitle:"",ogDescription:"",ogImage:"",twitterTitle:"",twitterDescription:"",twitterImage:""}},site:{id:"Site",siteMeta:{title:"C-Zone Entertainment",subtitle:"Premiere DJs & Musicians | Servicing Greater Boston & New England | 617.320.0723"}}},pathContext:{id:"a40173e1-9745-53df-b894-83108e83162e"}}}});
